 it but .. ): use 2 cani for 1 torpor and the 2*184 dmg you used for 2 cani will make 92*2 mana so 1 torpor .. torpor is 6 tick ( or 4 don t remember ) and 1k2 heal.. so you can solo allmob who don t make more domage than 1k2-2*184 = 850 dmg in 6 tick once slowed .. a frog of seb make about 200 dmg. that not finish: with fungie and regrowth natural regen AA regen you add 60 heal / tick <br>So you can solo all mob who don t hit more than 6*60 + 850 dmg per 6 tick = 1210 dmgs ...in melee.<br><br>So you don t loose mana .. you win Hp and mob die .. Use dot epic too and personaly i m using PoX of The Berteroluxx just make a littel more cani.<br>The biggest i soloed is Adjudant of Kael arena Trooper too .. dragons in WW .. dragons construct in DN .. gorenga shaman in maiden .. very fun fights, and i m far to be an ubber shaman. For bigs mobs don t pull with slow, it will be resisted, pull with malo then run FASTTT to be out of range cast of slow, then cast slow when mob run on you, he will be slowed before comming on you ( if resisted rerun and retry ) If you haven t place to kitte mob to slow it: 1st cast torpor on pet/ malo / pet attack / slow very fast, once slowed RUN on mob to get hits or pet will die fastly ( i use it for dragon in WW ).<br><br>That the best way i found to solo fast and a lot of mob.<br><br>kiki oracle of karana.<br><br>If you have any question emqil me if i can make something i will help you )p<br><br>&nbsp;<br>KiKi, Oracle Iksar of Karana serveur.<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=136450" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=136450</a> </td></tr>
