	   <tr><td colspan=2>Wisdom first, then stamina, as that will determine your total HP, and later on HP=mana.&nbsp;&nbsp;At least that's what I would recommend.  When I did mine I did WIS and STR, because I mistakenly thought STR was the determining stat for HP.<br><br>You may wonder why I don't say STR at first, since a Shaman starts off as pretty much a tank with magic, but this changes as you go up in level.<br>&nbsp;<br>______________________________________<br><b>Dargadin, Barbarian Shaman of the 53rd Season</b><br>Darg&nbsp;&nbsp; 41 Barb Warrior<br>Cyrius 21 Eru Wizard<br><b><span style='color: blue;'>Legions of Ragnorak</span style='color: blue;'><br>Ayonae Ro Server</b></td></tr>
