	   <tr><td colspan=2>At lvl 10, as at any other lvl, where is best to hunt is dependent on what you want.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>If you are a twink, then getting exp is most important, and you should hunt zones that have mostly animal mobs.  If you are not a twink, and you need to make money then you will want to kill the humanoid type mobs.  <br>Another factor is if you intend to solo or are looking for a group.  <br>Everfrost can be a good zone untill most of the calf green out (high teens?).  Since you have PoP you can check out a lot of diffrent zone near all non-evil cities. <br>Also remember that for the most part the mobs in the older part of the world are easier to kill than those in the newer parts. <br>For the most part you should be ok in most zone located near cities.   <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
