	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, a Jaundice Bone Bracer.<br>It is a rare drop in Old Sebilis, one of the toughest dungeons in Kunark.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>It procs a cold-based DD, Winter's Roar.  <br>It procs at lvl 45.<br>It is Shaman Only.<br>It costs like 25,000pp as of last night int he bazaar on Ayonae Ro.<br>Favorite item to twink lvl 45 shamen with.<br><br>When I was a lvl 10, I did Black Burrow, the snake ledge.  After that I went to East Commonlands and hunted Orcs in groups, the North Ro and hunted Dervishes in groups.  As you approach 20, Paludal Cavers seems to be the spot for totally mad exp. <br><br>Hope this helps.<br><br>Oh, and no, you are not stupid.  You are asking for information you want and need, that's not stupid at all.  I run into acronyms all the time I still don't know.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Oct 29 09:06:32 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>______________________________________<br><b>Dargadin, Barbarian Shaman of the 53rd Season</b><br>Darg&nbsp;&nbsp; 41 Barb Warrior<br>Cyrius 21 Eru Wizard<br><b><span style='color: blue;'>Legions of Ragnorak</span style='color: blue;'><br>Ayonae Ro Server</b></td></tr>
