	   <tr><td colspan=2>Also keep in mind you can turn in polar bear pelts to the merchant Cindi (may have her name wrong but it's something along those lines.) She gives XP, tattered armour and faction too if I remember correctly. You can also turn in spider fungus to the Shaman guild. They give you a jar to put 8 or so in before handing them in for XP and faction. Be warned this lowers your faction with the rogues and that's not good when you want to go banking. Though doing it a few times shouldn't hurt.<br><br>Also the warriors guild accepts goblin beads. Talk to the girl in the arena and she will give you a bag to fit 6 goblin beads into. Good XP and faction with this quest. <br><br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234170" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234170</a><br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=235432" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=235432</a><br><br>Shadow of the Dragon<br>Tunare<br>(www.eqsod.com)</td></tr>
