	   <tr><td colspan=2>Generally kill all the wandering stuff at the ned of the Halas ramp, decaying skellies, wolves, polar bear cubs, spiderlings.&nbsp;&nbsp;This should get you up to 5 or so.  Also the ice goblin camp nearby.<br><br>If you see a skeleton with &quot;Vengeful&quot; in the name, go directly to the guards, do not pass go, do not get killed.  These guys are about lvl 10 and will aggro on anyone, even a lvl 60.  You WILL get killed by these guys a few times, just do a /loc before you die so you know where to find your body.  Stay near the guards.<br><br>For other bits of wisdom from other wise Shaman types, see Caster's Realm:<br><br><a href="http://eq.crgaming.com/playguides/default.asp?Class=shaman&amp;Category=1" target=_new>http://eq.crgaming.com/playguides/default.asp?Class=shaman&amp;Category=1</a><br>&nbsp;<br>______________________________________<br><b>Dargadin, Barbarian Shaman of the 53rd Season</b><br>Darg&nbsp;&nbsp; 41 Barb Warrior<br>Cyrius 21 Eru Wizard<br><b><span style='color: blue;'>Legions of Ragnorak</span style='color: blue;'><br>Ayonae Ro Server</b></td></tr>
