 are getting good XP using blind kiting, and I'd like to hear where and what mobs its posible with. I try to offer creative ways to kill mobs that work well for me, and judjing from the XP I get other people say Im doing prety good. Even the original strategy was very good, and I rated that post accordingly. <br><br>55 Ogre Luminary on Luclin server--Chaotic Winds--Baron Aggrok<br>     <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
